snippet.title: Diana and Roma - Kindergarten Graduation
snippet.description:
Roma and Diana goes to their Kindergarten Graduation. They have learned a lot and had an all around great time!  
Roma is graduating from his preschool today and celebrates moving up to 1st grade.
